tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE photo_editing_history (
  edit_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  image_id UUID,
  change_description TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  editor_name TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE photo_history (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    image_id INT NOT NULL,
    editor_id INT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    changes JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE images (
    image_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    image_title TEXT NOT NULL,
    image_url TEXT NOT NULL,
    image_size INT,
    image_format TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE editing_history (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    image_id INT,
    editor_id INT,
    changes_made TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE images (
    image_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    image_name TEXT,
    image_url TEXT,
    image_size INT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE PhotoEditingHistory (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    image_id INT,
    change_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    editor_name VARCHAR(100)
);
